data.description: Welcome home to this updated unit in Chelseaport! This turn-key unit offers 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom and natural light galore. With new hardwood floors, bathroom, exposed brick, and 9’ ceilings makes every square inch of this 954 square foot home exudes urban living.  Positioned perfectly, the unit's large windows  fill the space with natural sunlight during the day and the double paned windows do an excellent job of keeping out the sound. As an added bonus, there is in-unit laundry, a private deck, and 1 off-street parking spot. Immerse yourself in the vibrant energy of this urban oasis and explore all of the restaurants Chelsea has to offer. Right off of the Tobin Bridge providing easy access to Boston and right across from Admiral’s Hill.  Easy access to downtown Chelsea and 111 Bus Stop with a quick commute to Boston Logan, this is a truly remarkable place to call home.
